{"tid":495212,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"毒 男 坤 哥 夜 蒲 老 蘭","createTime":"2017-12-10T13:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T02:30:28.000Z","uid":35964,"like":4,"dislike":118,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b604f4aae14f5c701f910961ba55bab86f2ebd","tid":495212,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T13:31:13.000Z","msg":"吳業坤日前晚上難得不用工作，即與兩名男友人「全男班」前往中環夜蒲輕鬆一下，約凌晨12時，眾人各自手持飲品於酒吧外吹水兼四圍𥄫女，期間亦不時嘻嘻哈哈。<br />\n<br />\n當吳業坤同朋友傾得興起之際，突然有幾個打扮性感的女仔在他們面前經過，同行兩名男友人即上前搭訕撩女仔，不過對方完全冇反應，眼見朋友行動失敗，站在旁邊「睇表演」的吳業坤即不停大笑，其後三人轉場到另一夜店繼續消遣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171207/photo/bkn-20171207000020796-1207_00862_001_04b.jpg?20171207154247\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171207000020796-1207_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20171207154247&h=2b8ed259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171207/photo/bkn-20171207000020796-1207_00862_001_03b.jpg?20171207154247\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171207000020796-1207_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20171207154247&h=1a96e52e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0c051dd9fded93c5a380a9a3a20ea6275d27036","tid":495212,"uid":21423,"like":192,"dislike":7,"score":185,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T13:35:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9436f6b5abc38f7de362d4a50bcd0fc1f4fbe89","tid":495212,"uid":89999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T13:38:27.000Z","msg":"有搭訕既話會影唔到相？"},{"pid":"4adb36c858c4aa5d6bd9f46b03550cb9a6f5f4b3","tid":495212,"uid":65530,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T13:47:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f19a5144cf100d849e9d30947ca8630c0c1f47c","tid":495212,"uid":5843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"好撚大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal